BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:4NyDD9STaCLQmxV_E91sm
SUMMARY:How to Tell a Seabird's Tale: The Role of the Writer and Scientific
	 Illustrator
DTSTAMP:20260401T023623Z
DTSTART:20260507T013000Z
DESCRIPTION:Panel event\nJoin three Pacific Northwest artists — two writers
	 and one illustrator — to learn how they distill their research on our loc
